            "text": "It can , in a unified way , exploit and utilize implicit feedback information , such as query logs and immediately viewed documents . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Moreover , our approach can implement result re-ranking and query expansion simultaneously and collaboratively . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
